Package org.mmbase.applications.editwizard Description

This package contains the classes used by the Editwizards to pass commands to MMBase. The classes maintain the xml documents that contain the MMbase data and editwizard forms.

This application makes use of the Dove classes.

Since:
MMBase-1.6
